data.description: Charming plantation style 3 bedroom 2 bath home located in Wahiawa Town. Remodeled in 2017, this home offers plenty of room to expand and customize to your heart’s desire. Home is conveniently located near the botanical garden and community park and within walking distance to shopping, school, and bus stop.  Schofield Barracks, Wheeler Army base, Dole Plantation, and the famous North Shore are just minutes away. The perfect place to start a family and enjoy Hawaii.
